      "text": "\"Tools\" embraces all four quadrants of the dance of knowing: *conceptualisations and coded descriptions* (eg valueflows), *narratives*, *skills* (eg means of using tools, and learning to use tools) and *genres* (rituals and festivals, places of obligatory participation, cycles of practice, etc.) The various DisCO ‘dances' are important loci for tools to be installed: see below.\n\n"
