    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "92621d937e99a4b6",
      "text": "- Method family codesigns an **architecture of tools** that is capable of effectively infrastructuring these particular patterns. \n- Method family **co-pilots** the tools\n- Method family **co-inducts** the tools.\n- Method family **co-reviews** the tools.\n- Repeat as required. Modify the pattern language too, of course, as new features of practice come into awareness."
